org.sakaiproject.assignment.api

Interface Assignment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable, Entity
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AssignmentEdit
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseAssignmentService.BaseAssignment, BaseAssignmentService.BaseAssignmentEdit

    public interface Assignment
extends Entity, Comparable

    Assignment is an interface for the Sakai assignments module. It represents a specific assignment (as for a specific section or class).

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  Assignment.AssignmentAccess
      AssignmentAccess enumerates different access modes for the assignment: site-wide or grouped.
